Accounting for ocean impacts nearly doubles the social cost of carbon
                    Bernardo A. Bastien-Olvera 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-3734-42671,2,3,4,5, Octavio Aburto-Oropeza 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-8173-14321, Luke M. Brander6,7, William W. L. Cheung 
